Class Message<C extends MessageContext,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.protocols.rpc.Message<C,T>

  • public final class Message<C extends MessageContext,T>

    Exchange object between a client and the server. Encapsulates all the required information for encoding the invocation and result of the RPC call.

    • Field Detail

      • UNKNOWN_ID

        public static final UUID UNKNOWN_ID
        ID to use for Error messages which to not have a known identifier. This is often used for when errors occur outside of the normal SNARL transport, such as in SSL negotiation that still must be reported back to the client.
